high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand between the coffee table and sofa, facing the sofa.
Pick up the keys from the rightmost cushion of the sofa.
Turn around, pass the television, and stop in front of the small black table with an open box on top.
Place the keys in the open box on the table.
Pick up the box with the keys in it from the table.
Turn around and carry the box to the coffee table so you are facing the red sofa when you stop.
Place the box with keys inside on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with keys in it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the red couch.
Pick up the keys that are in front of you.
Turn around and walk until you're even with then small black table to the right of the tv and when you are turn left and walk to it.
Put the keys in the box on the table.
Pick up the box.
Turn around and walk to the middle of the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the right side of the red couch.
Pick up the set of keys off of the seat of the couch.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and begin walking across the room, hang a left and walk up to the small black table.
Put the set of keys in the cardboard box on the small black table.
Pick up the cardboard box with the keys in it off of the table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Put the cardboard box with the keys in it on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with keys in it on the coffee table.
